  "spans": [
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0002",
      "text": " 89",
      "bbox": [
        521.04,
        723.59,
        534.92,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0003",
      "text": "4.2.32.3  Request Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        227.06,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0004",
      "text": "The Payload in FDISC and the corresponding LS_ACC are, except for the ELS_Command, identical",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        82.97,
        540.07,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0005",
      "text": "to the Payloads in FLOGI (see 4.2.7) and the LS_ACC (see 4.3.2).  When the S_ID of the FDISC",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        94.97,
        539.52,
        106.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0006",
      "text": "ELS is equal to zero, the FDISC ELS shall transfer an N_Port Name and node name, and request the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        540.0,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0007",
      "text": "assignment and login of an additional N_Port_ID.  The FDISC ELS with an S_ID equal to zero shall",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        539.98,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0008",
      "text": "only be sent by an N_Port with at least one N_Port_ID that is currently logged in with the Fabric, and",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        540.11,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0009",
      "text": "the assignment of an additional N_Port_ID shall not modify the Service Parameters between the two",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.96,
        539.96,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0010",
      "text": "ports.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.96,
        120.97,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0011",
      "text": "When the S_ID of the FDISC ELS is set to a previously-assigned N_Port_ID, the FDISC ELS shall",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        540.0,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0012",
      "text": "contain the N_Port_Name and node name corresponding to that N_Port_ID.  The interchange of",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        540.03,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0013",
      "text": "FDISC information shall not modify the operating environment or Service Parameters between the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        539.94,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0014",
      "text": "two ports.  Service Parameters contained in FDISC shall be ignored and no error condition shall be",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        539.93,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0015",
      "text": "reported.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        135.97,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0016",
      "text": "4.2.32.4  Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        214.86,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0017",
      "text": "When the S_ID of the FDISC ELS is zero, the D_ID field of the LS_ACC shall be set to the additional",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        539.96,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0018",
      "text": "N_Port_ID being assigned.  When the Fabric sends the LS_ACC, it shall consider Fabric Login to",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        539.98,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0019",
      "text": "have occurred for the additional N_Port_ID.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        298.96,
        288.24,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0020",
      "text": "When the S_ID of the FDISC ELS is not zero and is currently logged in, the D_ID of the LS_ACC",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        540.0,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0021",
      "text": "shall be set to the S_ID of the FDISC ELS.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        334.96,
        284.27,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0022",
      "text": "If an FDISC ELS with an S_ID set to zero is received by a F_Port Controller and no N_Port ID is",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        358.96,
        540.01,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0023",
      "text": "logged in, or if the S_ID is set to a non-zero N_Port_ID that is not currently logged, then an F_RJT",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        370.96,
        539.95,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0024",
      "text": "with the reason code set to ‘Login required’ shall be returned to the S_ID of the FDISC ELS if it was",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        382.96,
        540.02,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0025",
      "text": "issued in Class 1, or Class 2, and the FDISC ELS shall be discarded if it was issued in Class 3.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.96,
        515.94,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0026",
      "text": "4.2.33",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        123.78,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0027",
      "text": "Discover Address (ADISC)",
      "bbox": [
        133.78,
        418.96,
        259.23,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0028",
      "text": "4.2.33.1  Description",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.96,
        192.63,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0029",
      "text": "The ADISC ELS shall exchange addresses and identifiers of communicating Nx_Ports.  ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        484.84,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0030",
      "text": "4.2.33.2  Protocol",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        178.22,
        502.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0031",
      "text": "a) ADISC Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        514.96,
        200.73,
        526.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p108_s0032",
      "text": "b) LS_ACC or LS_RJT Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        538.96,
        287.89,
        550.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    }
  ],
